		<div id="home"> 
			<h3><strong>Welcome</strong></h3>
		FOUNDED in the late 1800s <strong>INLAND TITLE</strong> has been serving all of Idaho County with  customer based principles to guide us in every aspect of our work.  Going beyond giving a report, we excel in assisting customers with what they need to finalize their specific loan or purchase.  We specialize in residential and commercial title and escrow services, working with individual sellers, realtors, lenders and 1031 companies.  We are committed to building partnerships with buyers, sellers and lenders to handle each transaction with the care and the attention it deserves.  Our title department prides itself  on not just searching your land, but also helping you to resolve any issues that stand in the way of clear title. When you work with Inland Title, you are getting the very best title and searching information available! <br>
We don’t invent problems, we solve them.
<br><br>
Representing <strong>FIRST AMERICAN TITLE INSURANCE COMPANY</strong>, one of the most respected names in the title industry, we are local people committed to serving your needs with old fashioned courtesy, repsect and professional service.
<br><br>
If you are buying, selling or refinancing your property in Idaho County, do hot hesitate to call! 

		</div>
		<div id="long" style="display:none;">
			<h3><strong>Long Term Escrows</strong></h3>
			Inland Title provides local and immediate contract collection services for sellers or landlords.  We provide that impartial third party connection for your assurance of correct accounting of payments. Some of the benefits include:
<ul>
	<li>&nbsp;Economical setup and maintenance fees</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Original Documents safekeeping</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Accurate record keeping of all payments</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Complete year-end statements </li>
	<li>&nbsp;IRS reporting on qualifying accounts</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Tax and insurance payment options</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Local deposits of proceeds</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Recording of proper documents at close of escrow</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Dedicated staff with personal phone service</li>
	<li>&nbsp;Automatic payment options</li>
	</ul>

<br>

